# Apartment ERP — Environment Variables

**Copy to `.env` and fill in required values:**
```bash
cp .env.example .env
```

---

## REQUIRED — fill in before running

```env
DATABASE_URL=postgresql://postgres:REPLACE_WITH_DATABASE_PASSWORD@localhost:5432/test
NEXTAUTH_SECRET=REPLACE_WITH_32_BYTE_RANDOM_SECRET
NEXTAUTH_URL=http://localhost:3001
APP_BASE_URL=http://localhost:3001
```

---

## APPLICATION

```env
NODE_ENV=development               # development | production
COOKIE_SECURE=false             # true in production (HTTPS only)
CRON_ENABLED=true
OUTBOX_ENABLED=true
CRON_SECRET=REPLACE_WITH_CRON_SECRET
PORT=3001
```

---

## SECRETS

```env
AUTH_SECRET=REPLACE_WITH_32_BYTE_RANDOM_SECRET
INVOICE_ACCESS_SECRET=REPLACE_WITH_INVOICE_ACCESS_SECRET
FILE_ACCESS_SECRET=REPLACE_WITH_FILE_ACCESS_SECRET
```

---

## REDIS [OPTIONAL]

Redis is optional. Without it the app uses an in-memory rate limiter.
```env
REDIS_URL=redis://localhost:6379    # or redis://redis:6379/1 in Docker
```

---

## LINE MESSAGING [OPTIONAL]

Get credentials from https://developers.line.biz/

```env
LINE_CHANNEL_ID=REPLACE_WITH_LINE_CHANNEL_ID
LINE_CHANNEL_SECRET=REPLACE_WITH_LINE_CHANNEL_SECRET
LINE_ACCESS_TOKEN=REPLACE_WITH_LINE_ACCESS_TOKEN
LINE_USER_ID=REPLACE_WITH_LINE_USER_ID
```

---

## SENTRY [OPTIONAL]

```env
SENTRY_DSN=REPLACE_WITH_SENTRY_DSN
```

---

## BACKUP [OPTIONAL]

```env
BACKUP_CRON=0 3 * * *
BACKUP_RETENTION_DAYS=7
BACKUP_S3_BUCKET=REPLACE_WITH_BACKUP_BUCKET
AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID=REPLACE_WITH_AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID
AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY=REPLACE_WITH_AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY
AWS_REGION=REPLACE_WITH_AWS_REGION
```

---

## MONITORING

```env
METRICS_TOKEN=REPLACE_WITH_METRICS_TOKEN
GRAFANA_ADMIN_USER=REPLACE_WITH_GRAFANA_ADMIN_USER
GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD=REPLACE_WITH_GRAFANA_ADMIN_PASSWORD
```
